rComments: worst. class. ever. didnt help that he was more focused on making sexual references to everything than actually helping us understand the material.

Vargas is engaging and well-prepared.  he keeps it interesting and i've never liked the material he taught, but i was always interested and i genuinely enjoyed lecture.  deep respect for him, and he's very helpful and friendly!

Vargas was really chill. I had him for the intro seminar Fall 2006 called the Psychology of Advertising. Read the books and connect the papers with the reading. The class was long but he's a really smart and cool guy. He likes when you speak up and tell him different things about you. Really intelligent dude. Weird but smart.

this man is a great teacher, is funny, helpful, clear, and last but not least, he's a hottie.  my only complaint of the class is that i  sometimes wasn't able to concentrate because i was staring at his charming smile.  if only he wasn't married...
His class is so refreshing... tells the best stories. But the class is still hard!
